Name: breast pericanalicular fibroadenoma
Definition: A breast fibroadenoma that is characterized by stromal proliferation around epithelial structures.

Name: breast intracanalicular fibroadenoma
Definition: A breast fibroadenoma that is characterized by stromal proliferation compressing the epithelial structures into clefts.

Name: breast giant fibroadenoma
Definition: A breast fibroadenoma that is larger than 5 cm.
